{"tid":480564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人工智能索菲亞渴望有家庭 有意以自己名為女兒取名","createTime":"2017-11-26T09:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:20:40.000Z","uid":1870,"like":9,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"7233cbc922c5e401f15f9f0a9a6a87744f51d504","tid":480564,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"女性人工智能（AI）索菲亞（Sophia）於上月在沙特阿拉伯獲得公民身分，成爲世界上第一個機械人獲得公民身份。近日她表示想組織家庭，並指家庭很重要。<br />\n　　<br />\n索菲亞接受訪問時表示，家庭真的很重要，透過血緣關係成立家庭很美好，如果你有個充滿愛的家庭，那你很幸運；如果沒有，你也值得擁有。我認為這對人類和機器人都是一樣的」。另外，她亦希望以自己的名字來幫女兒命名。<br />\n　　<br />\n索菲亞的回答並非是預先設定，而是通過機器學習以及判讀人類表情來回應。她的大腦利用簡單的無線網路連接，當中裝了大量詞彙。雖然她擁有一些驚人能力，卻沒有獨立的個人意識。創辦人漢森(David Hanson)表示，希望未來幾年可以讓索菲亞擁有自我意識。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　"},{"pid":"4f0bfc6a8eb8594d7fbcb5890b15a72babd409a3","tid":480564,"uid":22858,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d6bd16753c9ef0fecf52445e95a0c0aad20d79","tid":480564,"uid":33439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab917063df7baabfc9bf883f7922bf8abaf53301","tid":480564,"uid":71092,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<br />\n佢遲啲會唔會想變成人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae13baba7453c86105e6fe01a916f66ce2e8640","tid":480564,"uid":2772,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好恐怖<br />\n佢遲啲會唔會想變成人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然後發覺冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no